subject: Horse Racing
Triple Crown (Horse Racing)
lead_paragraph: Shanghai Bobby, the Breeders’ Cup Juvenile winner, and the Delta Jackpot winner Goldencents lead the list of 369 early nominees for the Triple Crown series for 3-year-olds.
